last_episode_to_air.overview: Emma goes into labor after running into the woods. When she learns the truth, will she be able to save her baby? Or herself?

name: The Expecting
overview: Follow the dark journey of a young woman down on her luck and pregnant under mysterious circumstances. She must deal with the increasingly disturbing effects of her pregnancy and the potential conspiracy surrounding it.

episodes.name: Conception
episodes.overview: Emma wakes up alone. In the woods. With no clothes on. When she finds something is wrong, she sets out to discover what she can’t remember.

episodes.name: Options
episodes.overview: Emma visits her father for help in dealing with her pregnancy, but a trip to the doctor’s office forces her to open her mind about how to handle the situation.

episodes.name: Nesting
episodes.overview: Emma does her best to prepare for motherhood, including taking up swimming. But something sinister may be lurking within the water.

episodes.name: Inside
episodes.overview: Emma is getting her life in gear. New job. New car. But whatever is inside of her seems hell-bent on keeping her off track.

episodes.name: Daughter
episodes.overview: After an altercation with her dog, Emma starts having terrifying nightmares. Could they be a warning of what’s to come?

episodes.name: Father
episodes.overview: Emma tells Ty about her mom’s schizophrenia. After having a strange flashback during a moment of intimacy, Emma starts to question her own sanity.

episodes.name: Side Effects
episodes.overview: Emma meets with another girl experiencing similar symptoms to hear her story. When she returns to the woods to look for answers, her paranoia starts to grow stronger.

episodes.name: Bed Rest
episodes.overview: Emma is detained in Dr. Green’s office due to a problem with her pregnancy. Faced with serious doubt, she’ll do anything necessary to escape.

episodes.name: Late Term
episodes.overview: After a daring escape, Emma runs to her father for help and learns more about her mother. She’s ready to risk everything to escape a similar fate.

episodes.name: Arrival
episodes.overview: Emma attempts to get an abortion to end her suffering. But when the procedure goes awry, she suspects that everyone is out to get her.

episodes.name: Maternity Leave
episodes.overview: Emma goes into labor after running into the woods. When she learns the truth, will she be able to save her baby? Or herself?
